<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>DRUG BROCHURE </TITLE>
<HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor = "#150567" text="#FFFFFF" link="#ff0000">
<P>
<center>
<B><FONT SIZE = 8 COLOR = "#FF0000"> RECLAIMING THE WAR ON DRUGS <BA></FONT></B>
<P>
<blockquote>
<P>
<blockquote><blockquote>"Our drug problem will continue to get worse until we once again pursue responsible, intelligent and tough-minded policies.  We have the means; it is simply a question of whether we have the will."<br>
--William J. Bennett</center></blockquote></blockquote>
<P><UL>
<li>  The U.S. should treat the drug trade as a form of international terrorism.  Source countries that do not root out drugs must suffer clear penalties; and those countries fighting narco-terrorists within their borders must be assisted.
<P>
<li>  Put the U.S. military in charge of stopping the flow of drugs through the transit zone, will all interdiction agencies operating under their control.
<P>
<li>  Cut the flow of drugs across the U.S.-Mexican border with the aid of the military and the National Guard.
<P>
<li>  Toughen federal law enforcement against drug trafficking.  Establish clear priorities and hold authorities responsible for meeting them.  Stiffen federal marijuana penalties.
<P>
<li>  Allow funding for effective, religious-based programs with proven records.  Addicts in treatment at public expense must face rigorous programs and real sanctions for failure to complete them.
<P>
<li>  The national effort against drugs must be directed by strong, visible presidential support which utilizes the bull pulpit to send a clear, forceful message of zero tolerance toward drug use.
</UL><P>
<TABLE>
<tr><td><img src="/empower/attitude.jpg" align=top></td>
<td col width=300><center> "Im worried that for the first time in many years, tolerance for drugs is creeping back and that the momentum we had against drug use has been lost.  How could we have forgotten so quickly?  Why is it we no longer hear the condemnation against drugs coming from our leaders and our culture?"<br>
--Nancy Reagan<br>
   March 1995</center></td></tr>
</TABLE>
</blockquote>
</BODY>
<p><br>
<center>
| <a href = "/empower/">Home</a>
|</center>
<p><br>
