<DOCOLDNO>IA057-000936-B023-263</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/empower/drug-abandon.html 204.71.237.74 19970109172926 text/html 4290
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 17:29:33 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 27-Nov-96 16:11:00 GMT
