<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<TITLE>JOHN VON KANNON -- Heritage </TITLE>


<H3>JOHN VON KANNON</H3>
<HR>
<B>VICE PRESIDENT AND TREASURER</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/vonkan.gif" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Von Kannon is the former Publisher of The American Spectator, for which he now serves as a Contributing Editor. He previously served as Vice President of the Pacific Legal Foundation in Sacramento and President of Russell & Von Kannon, a Chicago-based marketing and consulting firm. A graduate of Indiana University, Von Kannon is a Senior Fellow at The Foundation for Research on Economics and the Environment, Bozeman, Montana.

<BR><HR WIDTH="30%"><BR><CENTER><A HREF="/heritage/hbut.map"><IMG SRC="/heritage/hbut.gif" ISMAP BORDER=0></A></CENTER></BODY>
</HTML>
