<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/claremont/edit/restcon.htm 204.71.237.74 19970108100810 text/html 6824
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 10:08:24 GMT
