<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/congress/intro.html 204.71.237.74 19970109164621 text/html 6285
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 16:46:33 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 23-Sep-96 19:41:05 GMT
Content-length: 6100
