<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Americans for Tax Reform </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<P>
<CENTER><a href="/atr/">home</a> | 8 of 8 | <a href="/atr/tax-presentation/bredoped.html">previous</a><br><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/paybeer.html"><FONT SIZE=6>The average cost of a bottle of beer
is 77 cents</a><BR>
<p>
<img src="/atr/sept96/New-2.gif">
<p>
</FONT></B></U></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><U><B><FONT SIZE=5>Taxes Imposed on Beer Production and
Sales<BR>
</FONT></B></U></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Federal Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Excise Taxes </FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Sales Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Federal Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Federal Payroll Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Workmen's Compensation Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>State Property Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Unemployment Insurance Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Local Property Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Local Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Local Sales Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Gas Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Tire Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Truck Highway Use Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Heavy Truck Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=4>Telephone Excise Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
