http://www.cpac.org:80/atr/tax-presentation/paygas.html 204.71.237.74 19970109193413 text/html 5258
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 19:34:26 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 30-Sep-96 19:35:53 GMT
Content-length: 5073
