<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/dept_writeups/bb996.html 204.71.237.74 19970109163009 text/html 16901
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 16:30:17 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 01-Nov-96 21:39:39 GMT
