"Homosexuals and the 10% Fallacy," <I>The Wall Street
Journal</I>, March 3, 1993, p. A14, and Edward O. Laumann, John
H. Gagnon, Robert T. Michael, and Stuart Michaels, <I>The Social
Organization of Sexuality</I>, The University of Chicago Press,
1994. 
</ol></font>

<p>

<center>
<b>
[<a href="/townhall/FRC/infocus/">Other Infocus</a>] 
[<a href="/townhall/FRC/policypapers.html">Other Policy Papers</a>]
[<a href="/townhall/FRC/reproduce/reproduc.html">Reproducing This 
Article</a>]
</b>

