<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/FRC/infocus/if95k8ed.html 204.71.237.74 19970109160510 text/html 3805
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 16:05:29 GMT
