<TITLE> The End </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">








<CENTER><img src="/townhall/banner-g.gif"><p></CENTER>
<h5><a href="/townhall/infotain/th_tour/end.html.cgi/textonly">[Text View]</a></h5>
<br>
<H2>The End</H2>











Whew!  We've reached the end of this little tour. <p>

Remember to submit your entry in the<A HREF="/townhall/infotain/th_tour/seldy.html#contest"> "Where in the world did the name Seldy come from"</A> contest.  We hope to add little things like this each week.  Some will be a little odd, others will be more serious.  Look for next week's installment when we show you the highlights from Town Hall's exciting launch on the Internet featuring Speaker Gingrich and Senator Dole.<p>
Please come back to see us often.  Tell your friends that if they do so life will be extra zesty! <p>

