HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:50:40 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Mar-96 18:20:49 GMT
Content-length: 7058
Content-type: text/html
