<TITLE> Chris Bertchie </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">
<center>[ <A HREF ="jon.html">Previous</A> | <A HREF ="pres.html">Next</A>
]<br></center><br>
<!-<IMG SRC="..." HSPACE=10 VSPACE=10 align = left>->
<center><H2>Chris Bertchie </H2>
</center>
<blockquote>
Chris Bertchie, Advertising Director, divides her time between planning and purchasing print and online advertising for Town Hall, and pursuing and placing advertising on the Town Hall site.  If you've enjoyed the added color, options, and
movement of banner advertising, or if you find it distracting, you have Chris to
thank.  She arrived at Town Hall via advertising, publishing, and ad agency
positions in New York, San Francisco, and Denver. These days, when not surfing
the Web, she can be found on the Chesapeake Bay, fishing or just cruising around
Annapolis aboard a classic wooden Viking Sportfisherman.
<P>
<a href="mailto:chris@townhall.com">chris@townhall.com</a>
